Package sg.edu.ntu.cz2002.grp3.Entity

Class Index

java.lang.Object
sg.edu.ntu.cz2002.grp3.Entity.Index
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Index
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Represents an index of a course. Contains a list of its lessons. Also keeps track of students registered under it and students waiting to be registered
Author:
Guat Kwan, Wei Xing, Ashton, Yi Bai, Zhe Ming
